"smart_blocks:Sessões/2026-04-13.md#Roadmap — Tudo que você faz agora --- ## 1. Suspensão → Nunca `Win + R` → digita `powercfg.cpl` → Enter Clica em **\"Alterar configurações do plano\"** no plano ativo Muda os dois campos **\"Colocar o computador em suspensão\"** para **Nunca** Clica **Salvar alterações** --- ## 2. Windows Update → Horas ativas `Win + I` → **Windows Update** → **Opções avançadas** → **Horas ativas** Muda para **Manual** → define o horário que você trabalha (ex: 07:00 às 23:00) --- ## 3. Obsidian — File Recovery Abre o Obsidian → `Configurações` (ícone de engrenagem) **Plugins principais** → procura **\"File Recove…": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":"1bojam9","at":1776111048120},"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.07117618,-0.01305669,0.09740083,-0.03294218,-0.01805239,0.04576829,-0.08106607,0.01639306,0.00551024,0.01833379,-0.00522305,-0.07898494,-0.02947041,0.00267797,0.02543344,-0.01816424,-0.04365732,0.02306547,-0.01244674,0.0256289,0.1324783,-0.00631518,-0.02680268,-0.03427122,0.00398969,0.01930741,0.01494384,-0.0014637,-0.08984396,-0.21394388,-0.00736298,-0.01493775,-0.02093903,-0.03086798,-0.02411914,-0.02546027,-0.02248516,0.04759182,-0.03527252,-0.00521517,-0.02578955,-0.00052113,-0.05872684,0.00205477,-0.07969722,-0.10756131,-0.01469644,-0.0189488,0.00360271,-0.00969138,-0.01211073,-0.02742629,-0.05371059,0.01907485,0.03912671,0.01278517,0.01450417,0.02487893,0.04529525,0.03261866,0.08627607,0.04884492,-0.23317184,0.07462607,-0.00819825,-0.00296549,0.00762714,-0.00889815,-0.00290343,0.04747884,-0.09272782,-0.03242475,0.03285603,0.05832988,0.08355317,-0.0015627,-0.06432266,0.01503642,-0.03885711,-0.01229466,0.02888863,0.12043039,-0.01745758,-0.0265795,-0.04353379,-0.06812544,0.0000462,0.01200465,0.00711453,0.00346637,-0.05535172,0.01672775,0.07553317,0.06001955,0.01050729,-0.00393087,-0.03110605,0.04504286,-0.04859517,0.08860535,-0.03638895,-0.01601352,0.0278071,-0.03002814,0.01949762,-0.02516898,0.00455636,-0.02206654,-0.019