"smart_blocks:Sessões/2026-04-13.md#Roadmap Completo --- ## 1. Suspensão → Nunca `Win + R` → digita `powercfg.cpl` → Enter Clica **\"Alterar configurações do plano\"** ao lado do plano ativo Muda os dois **\"Colocar o computador em suspensão\"** para **Nunca** Clica **Salvar alterações** --- ## 2. Fast Startup — Desativar Na mesma janela do passo anterior, clica na seta voltar até chegar em **\"Opções de energia\"** Clica **\"Escolher a função dos botões de energia\"** no menu esquerdo Clica **\"Alterar configurações não disponíveis no momento\"** **Desmarca** \"Ligar inicialização rápida (recomendado)\" Clica **Salvar alterações** --- ##…": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":"1y05lsr","at":1776111541128},"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.06114579,-0.03511752,0.02892254,-0.02630824,-0.01641815,0.04674596,-0.06774206,0.01307656,0.02822299,-0.00189714,-0.00502179,-0.09099919,-0.01696868,0.01812711,0.05773401,-0.03389152,-0.02579067,-0.02263677,-0.00887118,0.01304517,0.09893887,-0.00539077,-0.03611408,-0.07249275,-0.00771953,0.01713102,0.04233101,-0.02019815,-0.09312874,-0.20106192,0.0267065,-0.02187583,0.04146152,-0.07447369,-0.04835172,-0.00278178,-0.04354678,0.0205611,-0.06292998,-0.02508452,-0.01537695,0.01117424,-0.0277599,0.02707223,-0.0659453,-0.09463343,0.00747756,-0.0002457,0.00342221,-0.01308198,-0.02077353,-0.02798928,-0.0135263,-0.01141527,0.05530074,0.0630747,0.02953805,0.00092659,0.08077913,0.04121878,0.0711363,0.02420316,-0.22566861,0.06220861,-0.03044764,-0.01439659,-0.00395104,0.00262069,-0.01057149,0.06784151,-0.07745228,-0.02407363,0.04409113,0.07278572,0.07950993,0.021668,-0.06745236,-0.01877594,-0.03634611,0.01267232,0.03480737,0.10551646,-0.04655254,-0.05065397,-0.03927677,-0.01874232,0.00005362,-0.01750029,0.0019805,0.01463662,-0.03586489,0.02832722,0.05813595,0.04643089,-0.03699457,0.01026314,-0.02641549,0.04881931,-0.06464642,0.07780836,0.00089866,0.01642324,0.06634542,-0.00162497,0.04782166,-0.02352891,0.04244768,-0.0312677,-0.01